			<para>Given the sequence <latex magnify="yes">(a_n = 3n)</latex>, find the first 5 elements of the tail end beginning with <latex>N=1,000,000</latex>.</para>
			<math.display>
				<latex>n\from \NNr \longrightarrow \NNr,\quad n(i):= i^2</latex>
